subject: Textui.TestRunner regarding
msgSnippet: Hello, I m using JSDK 1.4 and Junit 3.7 on Win 98. And When I try to run junit.textui.TestRunner from the command prompt, I m getting an Exception in thread
messageBody:
Hello,

I'm using JSDK 1.4 and Junit 3.7 on Win 98. And When I try to run junit.textui.TestRunner from the command prompt, I'm getting an Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: MoneyTest (wrong name: junit/samples/money/MoneyTest).

Whereas, junit.swingui.TestRunner is working fine.

I've checked the CLASSPATH and it is set to junit/samples/ and junit/samples/money and junit/junit.jar. I am unable to reason, why I'm facing this problem.

Can anyone of you, please help me out.


Thanks,

Sreenivas
